BUGS:

Should cache the scaffolding built for the last $(D subseq) in
thread-safe storage so it is not rebuilt repeatedly.
*/
Iterator!(Range) findBoyerMoore(alias pred = "a == b", Range)
    (Range seq, Range subseq)
{
